//////////////////
html > main tag of website
head > All the links(Css,Js)
     > Except title nothing will be visible 
body > All the content of the website that is visible


Block
> They always start from new line
> Occupies the completed width of screen
> p div h1
Inline
> Start in same line
> Only take the width of content
> span img a


/////////
Inline
styletag
stylesheet

Inline>styletag>stylesheet

Inline
{
    color:red;
    font-size:30px;
}

styletag
{
    color:orange;
    height:300px;
    border-radius:40%
}

stylesheet
{
    height:400px;
    font-size:40px;
    width:200px
}

{
    color:red;
    font-size:30px;
    height:300px;
    border-radius:40%;
    width:200px
}


